<h3>High-Value Service Keywords</h3>
<p>Each of these deserves a dedicated page on your website.</p>
<p><strong>Core services:</strong>
- Home care + [city]
- In-home care + [city]
- Senior care + [city]
- Elder care + [city]
- Companion care + [city]
