<h3>Family Caregiver Research Keywords</h3>
<p>These are the queries families type during the decision-making process. They have high intent and low competition.</p>
<ul>
<li>"Signs my parent needs home care"</li>
<li>"How to talk to a parent who refuses help"</li>
